# Switch to the trunk branch for main development\ngit checkout trunk\n\n# Create a new feature branch\ngit checkout -b feature/my-new-feature\n\n# Work on the feature, then commit changes\ngit add .\ngit commit -m "Implement new feature"\n\n# Push the feature branch to the repository\ngit push origin feature/my-new-feature\n\n# Create a pull request and merge it back to trunk after review\n# ...\n\n# Merge trunk to testing for staging deployment\ngit checkout testing\ngit merge trunk\n\n# Deploy testing branch to staging server\n# ...\n\n# After successful testing, merge to live for production deployment\ngit checkout live\ngit merge testing\n\n# Deploy live branch to production server\n# ...